git Access
----------
SEP provides access via github to the latest CLA code.

git web interface: <http://github.com/sep/cla>

Read-only git access: <git://github.com/sep/cla.git>

Please consult http://lumera.sangia.org/wiki/index.php/HOW-TO_check_out_SEP_applications_from_git
for instructions on setting up a development environment.

Note that you must rename config.TEMPLATE.inc.php to config.inc.php prior to
running the CLA installation script.
